wiki.content: XXXTENTACION previewed this song on his Instagram account in January 2018. The snippet was uploaded everywhere with the title “Beverly Hills.” This song is reminiscent of the style X used in his early career, many would call it his “screaming” flow. On a distorted beat, X showcases his raw, abrasive, screamo style sound. He uses a similar delivery on songs like “GNARLY BASTARD” and “FAILURE IS NOT AN OPTION.” 3 repeating numbers is a common theme for X. He did a song called “777” off of his collaboration mixtape Members Only, Vol. 3 and the song with Joey Bada$$ on this album is titled “Infinity (888)”. There may even be some significance to the song titled “$$$”. 555 means you’re going through a major life change. It can also signal that this big change is coming up ahead, so prepare for it now.
